<figureCitation box="[556,621,1933,1958]" captionStart="FIGURES 1 – 3" captionStartId="1.[151,264,1953,1976]" captionTargetBox="[201,1385,197,1927]" captionTargetId="figure@1.[201,1386,193,1932]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURES 1 – 3. Habitus. 1) Atrocalopteryx fasciata spec. nov., holotype male; 2) Atrocalopteryx fasciata spec. nov., paratype male; 3) Atrocalopteryx laosica, a male specimen from Vietnam (Sapa). Specimens shown at the same scale." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/226644/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="389">
